## Neutral background for honest color

Photo pages use a neutral gray theme with zero chroma. That prevents any hue bias from the UI bleeding into your perception of the image.

```css
/* Gallery pages desaturate the surface */
[data-page-type="photo-gallery"] {
  --surface-l: 0.85; /* slightly darker for contrast */
  --surface-c: 0;    /* no chroma → neutral gray */
  --primary-c: 0;    /* keep UI accents subdued */
}
```

This makes the white border “pop” and provides a consistent viewing environment across light and dark modes.

